'''Palpatine's office''' was an office in the [[Imperial Senate Building|Galactic Senate Building]] on [[Coruscant]] used by [[Naboo]] [[Senator]] [[Darth Sidious|Sheev Palpatine]]. It was decorated with pieces from his personal art collection, and deliberately laid out in such a fashion as to subtly discomfort visitors and discourage them from staying, as Palpatine was not interested in encouraging guests. It did not have a view of the [[Imperial Palace|Jedi Temple]].<ref name="Queen's Peril" />

